# C&I BESS Competition Analysis

Comprehensive database of Commercial & Industrial Battery Energy Storage System inverters (90-120kW) with technical specifications extracted from manufacturer datasheets.

## Quick Start

### View Company Products
```bash
cat data/companies/sofar.yaml
```

### View Product Details
```bash
cat data/products/sofar_sofar_100ktlx_g4_ess.yaml
```

### Load in Python
```python
import yaml

# Load company data
with open('data/companies/sofar.yaml') as f:
    company = yaml.safe_load(f)
    
# Load product specs
with open('data/products/sofar_sofar_100ktlx_g4_ess.yaml') as f:
    product = yaml.safe_load(f)
```

## Database Contents

- **14 manufacturers** - One YAML file per company
- **43 products** - Detailed specs with units (kW, mm, kg, °C, %)
- **78 ZEREZ variants** - 99% coverage of certified products
- **58 PDF datasheets** - Original source documents

## Structure

```
data/
  companies/     # 14 company YAML files
  products/      # 43 product YAML files with full specs
  
datasheets/      # 58 manufacturer PDF files
  
benchmark_results/
  benchmark_results_20251026_013531.csv  # Latest extraction
```

## Technical Specs Available

Each product includes:
- Power ratings (kW)
- Efficiency (peak, Euro, CEC %)
- Dimensions (mm) and weight (kg)
- Electrical specs (voltage, MPPT count, THD)
- Environmental (temp range °C, cooling)
- Data source & confidence

## Session Management (Memory-Bank)

Resume work seamlessly across sessions:

```bash
# See where you left off
python3 scripts/memory_bank/resume_session.py

# Update after completing tasks
python3 scripts/memory_bank/update_memory.py \
  --completed "Extracted 10 products" \
  --next "Validate data" "Update docs"
```

The memory-bank system automatically tracks:
- Current session state and progress
- Project statistics and file counts
- Git repository state
- Active goals and next steps

See [.memory-bank/QUICK_START.md](.memory-bank/QUICK_START.md) for details.

## ZEREZ Importer (Production Ready)

Automated import wizard for ZEREZ certification database with real-time filtering and PDF matching.

```bash
# Start the Next.js app
cd benchmark-app
npm run dev

# Visit import wizard
open http://localhost:3000/import/zerez
```

### Features
- ✅ **GraphQL-powered search** - 600x faster than HTML scraping (2s vs 30+ min)
- ✅ **Real-time filtering** - Power, voltage, certification, manufacturer filters
- ✅ **3-step wizard** - Filter → Import → Match PDF
- ✅ **Server-Sent Events** - Live progress streaming
- ✅ **8,000+ manufacturers** - Complete tenant database with autocomplete
- ✅ **Fuzzy PDF matching** - Automatic datasheet linkage
- ✅ **Type-safe APIs** - Full Zod validation

### Performance
- Search: 2-5 seconds for filtered results
- Import: ~2 seconds per product (HTML details)
- PDF Match: < 1 second for 100 products
- **Full workflow: ~3.5 minutes for 100 products**

See [docs/zerez/ZEREZ_IMPORTER_SETUP.md](docs/zerez/ZEREZ_IMPORTER_SETUP.md) for production deployment.

